  "content": {
    "prompt": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Which of the following correctly compares <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"K sub E\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"K sub E\" overflow=\"scroll\"> <mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"> <msub> <mi>K</mi> <mi>E</mi> </msub> </mstyle> </math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"K sub p\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"K sub p\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>K</mi><mi>p</mi></msub></mstyle></math></span></span>, and provides a correct justification?</p>\n\n<div class=\"table_wrapper\">\n<table class=\"tgroup cols:3 colsep:0 frame:none rowsep:0\">\n\t<colgroup>\n\t\t<col class=\"colspec align:center colname:col1 colnum:1 colsep:1 colwidth:35\">\n\t\t<col class=\"colspec align:center colname:col2 colnum:2 colwidth:60\">\n\t\t<col class=\"colspec align:left colname:col3 colnum:3 colwidth:300\">\n\t</colgroup>\n\t<thead class=\"thead\">\n\t\t<tr class=\"row rowsep:1\">\n\t\t\t<th class=\"entry colname:col1\">&nbsp;</th>\n\t\t\t<th class=\"entry colname:col2\">Comparison</th>\n\t\t\t<th class=\"entry colname:col3\">Justification</th>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</thead>\n\t<tbody class=\"tbody\">\n\t\t<tr class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col1\">A</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col2\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"K sub p is less than K sub E\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"K sub p is less than K sub E\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>K</mi><mi>p</mi></msub><mo>&lt;</mo><msub><mi>K</mi><mi>E</mi></msub></mstyle></math></span></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col3\">The total energy of the sphere-planet system is constant throughout the swing, and there is less potential energy in the sphere-planet system on the new planet.</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col1\">B</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col2\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"K sub p is less than K sub E\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"K sub p is less than K sub E\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>K</mi><mi>p</mi></msub><mo>&lt;</mo><msub><mi>K</mi><mi>E</mi></msub></mstyle></math></span></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col3\">The total energy of the sphere-planet system is constant throughout the swing, but a smaller fraction of the total energy of the system is transformed into kinetic energy on the new planet.</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col1\">C</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col2\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"K sub p equals K sub E\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"K sub p equals K sub E\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>K</mi><mi>p</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>K</mi><mi>E</mi></msub></mstyle></math></span></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col3\">The kinetic energy of the sphere is independent of the gravitational field strength.</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col1\">D</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col2\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"K sub p equals K sub E\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"K sub p equals K sub E\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>K</mi><mi>p</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>K</mi><mi>E</mi></msub></mstyle></math></span></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col3\">The speed of the sphere is doubled, and the weight of the sphere is halved on the new planet, so the kinetic energies are equal.</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n",
